frames.caption: A whimsical scene features a teacup designed like a globe, filled with steaming water that resembles an ocean. Miniature sailing ships float on the surface, creating a surreal maritime atmosphere. The cup is surrounded by cookies and coffee beans, adding a cozy touch.
frames.description: The image presents a creative and imaginative setting where a teacup is transformed into a miniature world. The cup, painted with a map of the Earth, contains steaming water with tiny ships sailing on it, evoking a sense of exploration and fantasy. The surrounding cookies and coffee beans enhance the warmth and comfort of the scene.

frames.caption: A whimsical scene features a steaming cup designed like a globe, with miniature ships sailing on its surface. The cup rests on a saucer surrounded by cookies, creating a surreal blend of fantasy and everyday life. The steam rising from the cup adds a sense of warmth and coziness.
frames.description: The scene is set on a rustic wooden table, where a cup resembling a globe is filled with steaming liquid. Miniature ships with tiny figures are seen navigating the 'ocean' on the cup's surface, while cookies are scattered around, adding a playful and imaginative touch.
